overview: Convict Darius Ferdynand seeks assistance from parole officer Brock Avery after being framed for a crime. Andy Banks offers favors when officer Scotty Riley executes a search warrant and finds his stash. Celebrity Johnny Riley catches production assistant Ethan Slade shooting a video of him masturbating. Disgraced soldier Brenner Bolton thanks his superior officer Markie More for petitioning for his reinstatement.
title: Uniformed Cocksuckers
